        <h2></h2>
        <h2>- These results are hard to ignore!</h2>
        <p>Various clinical studies which have been conducted by The Parma University and the Sapienza University of Rome, Italy, as well as Perm University in Russia, conclude that B-Cure Laser is highly efficient in treating acute pain!</p>
        <h2></h2>
        <h2>And what do the patients say?</h2>
        <p>Here are the results of a customer satisfaction survey we have conducted among B-Cure Laser patients:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>60% of patients who purchased B-Cure Laser have reported <strong>a major pain relief</strong>and could go back to their normal lives.</li>
          <li>-	Over 60% of the patients rated B-Cure Laser as one of the 3  <strong>most efficient treatments for pain. </strong>.</li>
          <li>-	The patients have become more satisfied with a prolonged use of B-Cure Laser. <strong> A 60% satisfaction was reported</strong>among patients who have been using the B-Cure Laser for over a year.  </li>
        </ul>
