    <div class="container">
      <h3>Testimonials:</h3>
      <div class="item">
        <div class="photo-wrap"><img src="./B-Cure Laser_files/photo-1-1.jpg" alt=""></div>
        <div class="content">
          <h4>Naomi G: I was a candidate for a knee replacement procedure, I couldn’t even climb up the stairs at home. Naomi G: I was a candidate for a knee replacement procedure, I couldn’t even climb up the stairs at home. </h4>
          <p>I was also a candidate for a carpal tunnel surgery. I work with ceramics and I play the flute. I couldn’t create anymore due to the pain. </p>
          <p>. I have tried out so many things – acupuncture, electrical stimulation, pills, creams, nothing helped.</p>
            <p>. I purchased the B-Cure laser and started treating my knee and my arm daily.</p>
            <p> After 7-10 days, I felt a significant relief and a month later there was no pain at all. Today, If I start feeling pain, I treat myself and it goes away immediately. I feel 10 years younger!</p>

          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="item">
        <div class="photo-wrap"><img src="./B-Cure Laser_files/photo-2-1.jpg" alt=""></div>
        <div class="content">
          <h4>Jacob A.: I suffer from spinal disc herniation and one day, after a very long flight, I came home and suddenly my back hurt really bad.</h4>
          <p>Back pain can ruin your entire day; you can’t sit, can’t stand up, can’t lay down, can’t get in and out of the car.</p>
          <p>I decided to purchase the device and I felt a gradual but fast relief within a week.</p>
            <p>Thanks to the B-Cure Laser I enjoy working and living my everyday life without thinking about pain. Yes, the back pain might come back in the future, but since I have the B-Cure Laser I am not afraid of it anymore.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="item">
        <div class="photo-wrap"><img src="./B-Cure Laser_files/photo-3.jpg" alt="איתן"></div>
        <div class="content">
          <h4>Ethan: I have been suffering from neck pain since a young age. I also had a back injury during my military service. I have tried to many different therapies, massages and creams to no avail.</h4>
          <p>I work in the kitchen all day long and the pain was killing me. I decided to purchase the device because I realized I had nothing to lose.</p>
          <p>Surprisingly, my condition got so much better in a short period of time. Eventually, it changed my life. The device helps me maintain my stressful routine while staying completely pain-free.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
